metadata.name: IMAGs
metadata.description:
I spent the last past two years and a half learning and working with Notch, I found a really cool community and knew a lot of designers and artists. With my first NFT, I want to celebrate my goal in this world by showing the best IMAGs that I've produced in the last years.
Like a business card or a portfolio, I want to set this moment in the blockchain.
This is the starting point of a lot of experimentation about Notch x Foundation.

3840x4320px
60fps
.mp4

Lorenzo Venturini
2022
